AUDIO: '&gt;&gt; That\'s the hearth loaf. Hard on the outside, completely soft within. Feel that. It\'s still warm from the bricks. One of these keeps a man full for 3 days on the trail.'

[01:08] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: '&gt;&gt; Fair enough. Show me how the machinery handles that grain. &gt;&gt; Follow me, then. Let\'s head inside the main mill before the afternoon wind picks up too much. Ah, look at that golden light hitting'

