AUDIO: 'We felt something. And we refused to disappear. &gt;&gt; Lip syncing with an existing audio file and an image of your choice has never been easier because now we have the LTX director node. Instead of adding just'

[02:25] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'one image, you can now guide your lip sync generations with multiple images or text prompt blocks. The most important part of the director node is that you can use any audio you have without trimming it first. You can simply expand'

[02:37] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'or shrink the audio file with your mouse, choose the exact part you want on the timeline, and the whole process becomes much easier and faster. You can find the pauses in the timeline and separate your chunks accordingly. Huge'

