VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'generate the image, and you can use a Z image turbo workflow to do that. To create more images with consistent characters while placing your subject in different settings, you can use models like Flux 2 client or Quen image edit if you\'re strictly using local models. If'

[03:15] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'you want faster and more consistent results, you can also use GPT image 2. That\'s exactly what I did when creating the images for this clip so I could fully focus on creating the video. However, if you want full creative'

